src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 Midday' game
04 Nov 2019, 18:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 4 Midday" game were:
6-0-6-3
(six, zero, six, three)
